            <div class="feed-item-listing span-19">   
                <h2 class ="item-listing-title">
                    <a href="/editorial/2014/apr/11/smart-property-ethereum">Beware of Geeks Bearing Formulas: When property becomes smart </a>
                </h2>
                <hr class="thin">
                
                <div class="feed-item-listing span-19">   
                    <div class ="feed-item-listing-row">
                        <div class = "feed-item-listing-row-details span-19">
                             
                                <p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="http://media.rhizome.org/blog/9233/Hyper-Geography.jpg" alt="" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: xx-small;">From Joe Hamilton, <em><a title="hypergeography" href="http://hypergeography.tumblr.com/post/9240867586/ultrazapping-darrellg">hypergeography</a>. </em>Sources: <a href="http://ultrazapping.tumblr.com/post/8254191956/pipco-green-blue-horizontal-2005-by-sandy" target="_blank">ultrazapping</a> and <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/darrellg/5281960204/in/set-72157600345884548" target="_blank">darrellg</a>.</span></p>
<p>If you thought cryptocurrencies were hard to understand, you probably want to sit down for your first introduction to smart property.</p>
                                    
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div> 
            </div><!--END FEED ITEM LISTING-->
        </div><!--END FEED ITEM-->

